  text:
  - Use WASD to move.
  - Move into an enemy to attack it.
  - The faster you are moving, the more damage you deal. Dash with SPACE to deal
    more damage.
  - LEFT-CLICK to grapple towards walls and enemies.
  - Move into a wall and press SPACE to wall-dash in the opposite direction. Wall-dash
    has no cooldown.
  - Hold RIGHT-CLICK to snap to an enemy. Choose a direction with WASD and release
    RIGHT-CLICK to perform a snap-dash. Snap-dash has no cooldown.
  - Performing a wall-dash or snap-dash quickly resets the cooldown of dash and grapple.
  - Attack the ghost until its lights go out!
  - Collect the ghost soul and use its soul power to cleanse the grey shrine.
  - Once a shrine has been cleansed, you can spend soul power to buy upgrades depending
    on the type of shrine.
  - When all grey shrines are cleansed, you can cleanse the king shrine to complete
    the level!
